{"id": "1521396155462717470", "channel_id": "1350058928020656178", "author_id": "411703528831188993", "author_name": "rhizaea", "content": "Here, the tense of Tulu's sentences are weird.\nLemuria already fell in the past, so the changes should be\n\"The end of Lemuria __was__ inevitable.\"\n\"From the very beginning, Lemuria __had__ been living in lies.\"", "timestamp": "2026-06-30T06:05:09.636000+00:00", "thread_id": "1350058928020656178", "attachments": [{"id": "1521396155118780416", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3445962, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1350058928020656178/1521396155118780416/image.png?ex=6a4556d5&is=6a440555&hm=420dbc8466f5d8a1842f68a9ce351c17810ff61ccc10d4ad8617189e06f1db7c&"}]}
