{"id": "1521582035670405311", "channel_id": "1350058928020656178", "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "content": "Problems with Realm Mastery descriptions.\nHow to access:\nWhen entering any Awakener's information screen, click the \"Details\" button next to their Attributes section.  In the new window that pops up, click the little information icon for Realm Mastery.\n\nIssue #1 - Mistranslation:\n\nIt currently states, \"When switching to 'Still Sea', the shield gained...\"\n\n\"Still Sea\" should be changed to \"Tranquil Sea\".\n\nIssue #2 - Missing or Incorrect Information\n\nIt currently states:  \"...the shield gained +0.01% of Max HP...\"\n\nThe problem is that this doesn't explain how Realm Mastery is involved in this calculation for the value of the shield gained.  I understand that the preceding statement introduces the concept of \"...for every 1 point of Realm Mastery...\", so should this instead read as follows:  \"...for every 1 point of Realm Mastery, the shield gained increases by 0.01% of Max HP...\" ?\n\nIssue #3 - Missing or Incorrect Information\n\nIt currently states:  \"...and Tentacle attacks triggered by Active DMG in 'Raging Waves' increase Tentacle DMG by 0.02%\"\n\nSimilar to Issue #2 previously, should this instead read as follows:  \"... for every 1 point of Realm Mastery, increase DMG by 0.02% for the Tentacle attacks triggered by Active DMG in 'Raging Waves' \"", "timestamp": "2026-06-30T18:23:46.931000+00:00", "thread_id": "1350058928020656178", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-30T18:24:13.437000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1521582033074258122", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-06-30_012132.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 4859882, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1350058928020656178/1521582033074258122/Screenshot_2026-06-30_012132.png?ex=6a455b32&is=6a4409b2&hm=8724e7ac0d5833725e22d222f8c99360d17854c120e2182b4276c16922acece4&"}, {"id": "1521582034148003940", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-06-30_012259.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2208941, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1350058928020656178/1521582034148003940/Screenshot_2026-06-30_012259.png?ex=6a455b32&is=6a4409b2&hm=3bc94355d63e1647de5cc9b94d470d03a76669466d00622bc851b2804bb1eb4b&"}, {"id": "1521582034672418957", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-06-30_012720.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2372349, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1350058928020656178/1521582034672418957/Screenshot_2026-06-30_012720.png?ex=6a455b32&is=6a4409b2&hm=836f0b6c24520d531d9feebf18219275983b662c3cb3f41c116fc772197d43c0&"}, {"id": "1521582035284656320", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-06-30_014450.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2380016, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1350058928020656178/1521582035284656320/Screenshot_2026-06-30_014450.png?ex=6a455b32&is=6a4409b2&hm=8d64712c2ca28880799e46c1d3db9676e282678891a9e6eb21855c2f27528bef&"}]}
